	<h1 class="title">《唐顿庄园》特供商，一个手套公司是如何活过238年？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/399912/small/399912.JPG?1452046699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张田小 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-19 08:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9709/medium/9709.jpg?1436674819" alt="" />			
	</div>
